com.exacttarget.etpushsdk.event

Class PushReceivedEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.exacttarget.etpushsdk.event.PushReceivedEvent

  • public class PushReceivedEvent
extends Object
    This event is posted via the EventBus. Register on the EventBus for this event type to see the data that ExactTarget received from their servers.

    Sent whenever a Push or Geofence message has been received and processed by com.exacttarget.etpushsdk.ETPushReceiver. You can listen for this event if you need to do something custom with the payload. Maybe you've sent custom key Attributes with a message and you can get at them by handling this message.
